quran[4{c,v,t}:
5,14,"isi terhan hum ne unn logon se bhi pukhta ehad liya tha jinhon ne kaha tha ke hum"" nasari"" hain, magar un ko bhi jo sabaq yaad karaya gaya tha is ka aik bara hissa onhon ne faramosh kar diya aakhir-kaar hum ne un ke darmain qayamat taq ke liye dushmani aur aapas ke bughz o inaad ka beej bo diya, aur zaroor aik waqt aeye ga jab Allah inhen betaye ga ke woh duniya mein kya banatay rahay hain"
5,15,"ae ahal kitaab! hamara rasool tumahray paas aa gaya hai jo kitaab Ellahi ki bohat si unn baton ko tumahray samnay khol raha hai jin par tum parda dala karte thay, aur bohat si baton se dar guzar bhi kar jata hai tumahray paas Allah ki taraf se roshni aa gayi hai aur aik aisi haq numa kitaab"
5,16,jis ke zareya se Allah taala unn logon ko jo is ki Raza ke taalib hain salamti ke tareeqay batata hai aur apne azan se unn ko andheron se nikaal kar ujalay ki taraf lata hai aur raah raast ki taraf un ki rahnumai karta hai
5,17,"yaqeenan kufar kya unn logon ne jinhon ne kaha maseeh Ibn maryam hi khuda hai ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se kaho ke agar khuda maseeh Ibn maryam ko aur is ki maa aur tamam zameen walon ko halaak kar dena chahay to kis ki majaal hai ke uss ko iss iraday se baz rakh sakay? Allah to zameen aur asmano ka aur unn sab cheezon ka maalik hai jo zameen aur asmano ke darmain payi jati hain, jo kuch chahta hai peda karta hai aur is ki qudrat har cheez par haawi hai"
